---
title: Eat the Rainbow Crunch Wraps with Bell Pepper, Guac, Black Beans & Feta
description: All the colors of the rainbow are rolled up in this beautiful plant-based wrap that you can eat right away or tuck into your lunchbox for later. A satisfying shmear of refried black beans on a warm tortilla is just the beginning; next you’ll dress crunchy cukes and bell pepper in a creamy avocado dressing dotted with salty feta cheese and seasoned with cilantro, lime, and chili flakes. Layer those veggies on the beans, roll up, and you’re ready to discover that pot of gold.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6509a259800a93f3a84c4ddd-28cf52b6.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6509a259800a93f3a84c4ddd.pdf
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 10 minutes
cuisine: North America
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/eat-the-rainbow-crunch-wraps-6509a259800a93f3a84c4ddd
nutrition:
